-- Italy stability committee to discuss Monte Paschi: sources
-- 
-- Mon Jan 28, 2013 4:57am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/01/28/us-montepaschi-derivatives-committee-idUSBRE90R09U20130128

 

 ROME  (Reuters) - Italy's financial stability committee, made up of representatives of the Bank of Italy, the finance ministry and regulators, will meet on Tuesday and will discuss the troubled Monte Paschi bank, sources close to the situation said on Monday. 
 The committee deals with cases potentially affecting Italy's financial stability. (Reporting by  Giselda Vagnoni )